      <title>香港交易所新任首席执行官押注大型IPO卷土重来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/hong-kong-exchange-s-new-ceo-is-betting-on-big-ipos-coming-back</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港交易所清算有限公司首席执行官表示，随着基本情况的改善和中国监管机构的帮助，预计大额首次公开募股将卷土重来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/hong-kong-exchange-s-new-ceo-is-betting-on-big-ipos-coming-back</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 01:36:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石集团的葛瑞预计增长将在通胀斗争中放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/blackstone-s-gray-sees-growth-slowing-as-fed-battles-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石公司总裁乔恩·格雷表示，由于顽固的通货膨胀会影响美联储开始降低借贷成本的能力，经济增长将会放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/blackstone-s-gray-sees-growth-slowing-as-fed-battles-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 01:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
